Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: MX funding agreed
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xkqb
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 31 Mar 1985
Job creation given as reason why vote on MX funding went Reagan's way. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.